The paper deals with image recognition experiments using deep neural networks, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses the performance of supervised classification tasks, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed similarity metric is based on the misclassification ratios of trained DNNs, which is a topic in neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper discusses the usefulness of the proposed method for classification problems, which is a topic in natural language processing (cs.CL).
